cardSentences.cardSentence: Do you feel sad this week?
Have you not been in contact with people in the last week?
Have you felt like giving up on a problem lately?
In the last week do you believe you have been supported by others?
Have others put you down this week?
Do you feel like your ideas are not being accepted?
Lately, Have you believed that your ideas are not taken into consideration?
Have you been more negative than positive of late?

cardForm.content: Life is 10% what happens to you and 90% how you react to it.
cardForm.author: Chuck Swindoll

cardForm.content: A really great talent finds its happiness in execution.
cardForm.author: Johann Wolfgang von Goethe

cardForm.content: Beginning today, treat everyone you meet as if they were going to be dead by midnight. Extend to them all the care, kindness and understanding you can muster, and do it with no thought of any reward. Your life will never be the same again.
cardForm.author: Og Mandino
